{
  "stem": "18520.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 504.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Germany, I didn't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't find anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened is I was going-- I was in a few camps where they keep the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The most was Munich, headquarters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a list there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I-- I-- I knew who was alive and who was dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew my sister maybe survived, maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew my brother is in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The rest, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what I-- I just looked, actually, for my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or I look just for Finkelstein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] When I went to Italy, I saw I have nobody there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't stay there, I didn't want to stay there no more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Italy, they picked in this camp over there, they picked a group that they can do things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Munich, that they can do the-- they are responsible, they are knowledgeable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They ask you what-- what-- where you come from, who's your father, what did you do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that-- so they picked me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- I-- even in Poland, I was a little-- a chalutz already when I joined the organization and everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had in mind something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to live in a commune.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was in my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I have nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went-- they picked a group of people, about 30 people, 35.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was-- we had three girls in it, and the rest was boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe this was people from Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Bricha, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For people-- the Bricha [? over ?] the Haganah, they-- they were together but it's two different--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was involved already to do some work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know yet nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we said that the plan is, I want to live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
